# F1 Telemetry & AI Race Engineer Dashboard - Frontend

Environment configuration for the Next.js/React frontend.
Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your actual values.

## API Configuration
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

## Application Settings
REACT_APP_NAME=F1 Telemetry & AI Race Engineer Dashboard
REACT_APP_VERSION=0.1.0

## Environment
REACT_APP_ENV=development

## Feature Flags
REACT_APP_ENABLE_MOCK_DATA=true
REACT_APP_ENABLE_AI_FEATURES=true

## Analytics (Optional)
# REACT_APP_ANALYTICS_KEY=your_analytics_key

## Debug
REACT_APP_DEBUG=true
